Cause-specific life years lost in individuals with treatment-resistant 
depression: A Danish nationwide register-based cohort study.

Madsen KB(1), Plana-Ripoll O(2), Musliner KL(3), Debost JP(4), Petersen LV(3), 
Munk-Olsen T(5).

Author information:
(1)National Centre for Register-based Research, Department of Economics and 
Business Economics, Aarhus University, Denmark; iPSYCH, the Lundbeck Foundation 
Initiative for Integrative Psychiatric Research, Denmark; MOODSTRATIFICATION- EU 
project 754740. Electronic address: kathrine.bang@econ.au.dk.
(2)National Centre for Register-based Research, Department of Economics and 
Business Economics, Aarhus University, Denmark.
(3)National Centre for Register-based Research, Department of Economics and 
Business Economics, Aarhus University, Denmark; iPSYCH, the Lundbeck Foundation 
Initiative for Integrative Psychiatric Research, Denmark.
(4)National Centre for Register-based Research, Department of Economics and 
