Hospital, Department of Neurology, Denmark.
(5)National Centre for Register-based Research, Department of Economics and 
Business Economics, Aarhus University, Denmark; iPSYCH, the Lundbeck Foundation 
Initiative for Integrative Psychiatric Research, Denmark; MOODSTRATIFICATION- EU 
