Bridging the age gap in breast cancer. Impacts of omission of breast cancer 
surgery in older women with oestrogen receptor positive early breast cancer. A 
risk stratified analysis of survival outcomes and quality of life.

Wyld L(1), Reed MWR(2), Morgan J(3), Collins K(4), Ward S(5), Holmes GR(5), 
Bradburn M(6), Walters S(6), Burton M(4), Herbert E(6), Lifford K(7), Edwards 
