Copenhagen, Copenhagen, Denmark.
(4)Department of Sociology, Vrije Universiteit Brussel, Brussels, Belgium.
(5)Department of Health Management. Lithuanian University of Health Sciences, 
Kaunas, Lithuania.
(6)Aging and health. Demographic Research Institute, Budapest, Hungary.
(7)Department of Sociology. Stockholm Centre for Health and Social Change, 
